          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_Membership_FindUsersByName",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve user information from a membership database based on a specified application name and a username pattern. It supports pagination, allowing the retrieval of a specific page of results. The procedure returns user details such as username, email, and account status, and it also returns the total number of users that match the criteria."
        }
